  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Suppress installation of unnecessary files:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed "s/ install-data-local//" -i doc/Makefile.in</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Prepare the package for compilation:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed "/DG_DISABLE_DEPRECATED/d" -i glade/Makefile.in &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix= \
            --disable-static</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Compile the package:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install the package:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>porg -lD "make -j1 install &amp;&amp;
rm -v /lib/libglade-2.0.la"</userinput></screen>

    <sect3>
      <title>Command Explanations</title>

      <para>
        <command>sed "/DG_DISABLE_DEPRECATED/d"</command>: Some of the glib
        functions that libglade uses were declared deprecated in glib-2.30.
        This sed removes the G_DISABLE_DEPRECATED CFLAG.
      </para>

    </sect3>

  </sect2>

